00226 template <class Product>
00227 void TSupplierCompWrap<Product>::EnsureWorkInitialized()
00228 {
00229        if (m_workStatus < ISupplier::WS_INIT){
00230               if (m_updateMode == SWM_EXPLICIT_INIT){
00231                      m_productChangeNotifier.SetPtr(this);
00232               }
00233 
00234               if (!m_areParametersValid){
00235                      m_areParametersValid = true;
00236 
00237                      OnParametersChanged();
00238               }
00239 
00240               if (InitializeWork()){
00241                      m_workStatus = WS_INIT;
00242               }
00243               else{
00244                      m_workStatus = WS_CRITICAL;
00245 
00246                      if (m_updateMode == SWM_EXPLICIT_INIT){
00247                             m_productChangeNotifier.Reset();
00248                      }
00249               }
00250        }

00254 template <class Product>
00255 void TSupplierCompWrap<Product>::EnsureWorkFinished()
00256 {
00257        if (m_workStatus <= ISupplier::WS_INIT){
00258               TSupplierCompWrap<Product>::EnsureWorkInitialized();
00259 
00260               m_workStatus = WS_LOCKED;
00261 
00262               if (!m_productPtr.IsValid()){
00263                      m_productPtr.SetPtr(new Product());
00264               }
00265 
00266               QElapsedTimer timer;
00267               timer.start();
00268 
00269               m_workStatus = ProduceObject(*m_productPtr);
00270               I_ASSERT(m_workStatus >= WS_OK);   // No initial states are possible
00271 
00272               m_elapsedTime = timer.nsecsElapsed() / 1000000000.0;
00273 
00274               switch (m_updateMode){
00275               case SWM_EXPLICIT_INIT:
00276                      m_productChangeNotifier.Reset();
00277                      break;
00278 
00279               case SWM_IMPLICIT_INIT:
00280                      m_productChangeNotifier.SetPtr(this);
00281                      break;
00282 
00283               default:
00284                      break;
00285               }
00286        }

00440        switch (m_parent.m_updateMode){
